(Google tarafindan cevrilmistir) Perakende magazanizin iade ve degisim politikasi nedir?

(Orijinal)
What is your retail store return and exchange policy?
featured_question.answer:
(Google tarafindan cevrilmistir) Lion's Den'de urun secimimizden, hizmetlerimizden ve destekcilerimize sagladigimiz egitimden gurur duyuyoruz. Ancak, bazen urunlerimizin cesitli nedenlerle hedefi tutturamayabilecegini anliyoruz. Satin aldiginiz urunle ilgili bir sorun varsa ve kusurlu olduguna inaniyorsaniz, satin aldiginiz urunun degisim icin uygun olup olmadigini ogrenmek icin orijinal satin alma tarihinden itibaren 30 gununuz vardir. Degisim yapilamiyorsa nakit para iadesi yapilmayacaktir; tum bakiyeler gelecekteki satin alimlar icin bir hediye kartina uygulanacaktir. Urunlerimizin dogasi geregi ve personelimizin sagligi ve guvenligi icin tum satislar kesindir. Satin alma isleminizin uygun olup olmadigini gormek icin lutfen degisim politikamiza bakin.

(Orijinal)
At Lion's Den, we take pride in our selection of products, our service and the education we provide our patrons. However, we understand that sometimes our products may miss the mark for a variety of reasons. If there is an issue with your purchase, and you believe it is defective, you have 30 days from the original purchase date to find out if your purchase is eligible for exchange. If an exchange cannot be made, no cash refunds will be issued; all balances will be applied to a gift card for future purchases. Due to the nature of our products, and for the health and safety of our staff, all sales are final. Please see our exchange policy to see if your purchase is eligible.
